{"tid":2222672,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實唔需要為留任離任嘈，當班粉人唔存在就得","createTime":"2020-09-29T08:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T16:12:42.000Z","uid":94771,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"d1a29023e9aad025d8b6460989ec64b03a3ec238","tid":2222672,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:49:34.000Z","msg":"老實講，開頭35+，已經應該係有共識，最後一次<br />\n真係玩埋最後一次，所以部份本土派都唔會太大反感，加上的確算係公平<br />\n<br />\n所以個時我都係大力支持初選，<br />\n<strong>之後結果就係，支那的確因為咁<span class=\"red\">DQ12，延後選舉</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n係個一下成條<span class=\"red\"><strong>議會戰線</strong></span>就死撚佐架啦<br />\n所以我開頭先咁反感佢地班泛民<strong>無所不用其極都要留任</strong><br />\n<br />\n永遠販賣假希望係議會戰線到，不惜出賣自己人格同尊嚴<br />\n唔認清條戰線死佐，永遠都唔會有進步<br />\n<br />\n依次民調其實同出千係無分別，因為佢地係將成個本土派意見拋走佐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k6DNWJx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk6DNWJx.png&h=94c01a1b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n請問咩叫中間派？點解本土派意見唔理，之後屌人分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，真神奇<br />\n<strong><ins>就算支那真係想分化，都係泛民自己衝入去比人分化依邊陣營</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">後尾諗通佐，反正議會戰線都死撚佐，死撚佐即係唔存在啦，大家就無視佢啦<br />\n反正對大家黎講佢的作用都係等於0</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>請大家都係留意返要注意的野啦</strong></span></span><br />\n十二手足<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TBSGgLW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTBSGgLW.jpg&h=562045eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/save12youthspetitions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fsave12youthspetitions&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=5887f5b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/save12youthspetitions</a><br />\n十二港人無人提？咁咪我開囉，但無人推呢？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2222381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2222381</a><br />\n<br />\n國殤。中秋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yegcop7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyegcop7.jpg&h=c8e02262&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/weVHLDt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FweVHLDt.jpg&h=59efe919&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5038529bbab08839e4b5ecd56bb86a84a1c2138","tid":2222672,"uid":72466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:49:44.000Z","msg":"撞"},{"pid":"ecf12d34a15ce5d8382ca35d02165569204773e8","tid":2222672,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:50:19.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"3ceed5f78e186f4dd856e3273732c64d8209996c","tid":2222672,"uid":72466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:50:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"951a43ea8ac25b31b4706b6f450bc12f94adac1f","tid":2222672,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6bdf1211890df5b2cae59350dcac213f291aa8","tid":2222672,"uid":339851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3158e43805cdd9070a5b673181fc6936eef0788e","tid":2222672,"uid":283912,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:51:07.000Z","msg":"我都冇興趣再理個班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地留定走其實都冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3d842bead4884160d91163487e3d30ad386c17","tid":2222672,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b437b9ecb5e2e35a7e9c