><br />\n<br />\n <span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>十月一 洗邋遢大行動日期：九月三十到十月一<br />\n細節：九月三十號日落之後將一件或多件嘅黑色衫掛出當眼處，例如：陽台，晾衫架，窗口，十月一號日落後收番所有衫<br />\n特殊情況：落雨嘅話就將黑色衫掛滿窗口<br />\n</strong></span></span> <br />\n<br />\n以行動話比全世界聽，我哋香港人係冇放棄，係一直都追求緊自由同民主！<br />\n<br />\n我哋要真普選，我哋要投票，我哋要民主！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YN5t8YM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYN5t8YM.jpg&h=4eb49fa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YjNXhR7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYjNXhR7.jpg&h=e2fc13e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(有口號嘅靚衫要收埋先，狗狗見到上你屋企吠你就唔好啦)<br />\n(住狗狗宿舍或者附近嘅手足都唔好掛)<br />\n<br />\n風險問題：<br />\n我覺得風險算低<br />\n有口號嘅靚衫唔掛，住狗舍或者附近嘅手足唔掛<br />\n1.應該冇人會特意數你屋企位置<br />\n2.就算數，都唔知咩人住入面<br />\n3.就算知，都唔知你係咪咁啱洗黑衫<br />\n4.就算知你屋企位置，知咩人住入面，知你係黃絲，佢都奈何唔到你<br />\n5.更何況好多人一齊做<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>一齊掛，叫曬所有人一齊掛！</strong></span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K1zrba2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK1zrba2.jpg&h=b001db63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白羅斯嘅朋友都用呢招！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TA6kZ4B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTA6kZ4B.jpg&h=35b07827&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接連幾個禮拜我都會大力宣傳，希望多多支持<br />\nTg Channel (純粹發佈消息用)<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEcuHqz2znXG5EWzLw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEcuHqz2znXG5EWzLw&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=21f1f0e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEcuHqz2znXG5EWzLw</a>"},{"pid":"604cc957ad6a4aef8a0200de6e7140c5e53acc59","tid":2222672,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:52:48.000Z","msg":"是但 留與不留對大局都無大影響"},{"pid":"d5e63e9c5da50567b4c0618dcd23c51378f48ba3","tid":2222672,"uid":263213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3158e43805